00:20:37.069 --> 00:20:39.905
(BEATBOXING)

344
00:20:43.158 --> 00:20:44.368
(CHUCKLING)

345
00:20:44.451 --> 00:20:45.869
Isn't Daddy really cool?

346
00:20:46.245 --> 00:20:47.829
