382
00:22:37.647 --> 00:22:38.982
MINSEO: What?

383
00:22:39.066 --> 00:22:43.820
Why does Mr. Song
want to see his parents?

384
00:22:49.576 --> 00:22:50.744
Mr. Song.

385
00:22:50.827 --> 00:22:53.372
Why did you tell Boseok
to bring his parents?

386
00:22:53.455 --> 00:22:55.582
What did Boseok do so wrong?

387
00:22:55.665 --> 00:22:58.752
Minseo, it's not just his parents.

388
00:22:58.835 --> 00:23:00.879
Your parents came last month too.

389
00:23:00.962 --> 00:23:03.131
