416
00:24:14.828 --> 00:24:17.539
MINSEO: Boseok is very kind, smart,

417
00:24:17.622 --> 00:24:21.251
cool and nice to his friends.

418
00:24:21.334 --> 00:24:22.961
-Yes.
-Yes.

419
00:24:23.044 --> 00:24:24.671
MINSEO: Boseok is very kind.

420
00:24:24.754 --> 00:24:26.631
He lent me money.

421
00:24:26.715 --> 00:24:29.384
Don't call his parents!

