stay outside forever?

510
00:29:41.529 --> 00:29:43.281
Okay. I'll get home early.

511
00:29:43.364 --> 00:29:46.242
Honey. I love you. I love you, darling.

512
00:29:47.160 --> 00:29:49.287
He's so simple.

513
00:29:50.830 --> 00:29:53.458
